Williams is 52. Actor Erik Estrada is 50. Actor Victor Garber is 
50. Actress Kate Nelligan is 48. Rock singer-musician Nancy Wilson 
(Heart) is 45. Golfer Hollis Stacy is 45. Actress Isabelle Huppert 
is 44. 
