	Wall St. Stocks Set Record  
</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- The Dow industrials bounded to a closing high  
today but stopped short of 10,000 as a new round of corporate 
mergers boosted stock prices. The Dow rose 82.42 to close at 
9,958.77. The Dow topped its previous record close of 9,897.44, set 
last Thursday. NYSE advancers led decliners 1,529-1,443. The Nasdaq 
composite index, driven by technology issues, was up 49.91 at 
2,431.44. 

