<HEADLINE>  Duke, SW Mo. State Win With Defense </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	CHARLOTTE, N.C. (AP) -- The difficulty of what's ahead hit Steve  
Alford even before the end of the party marking the biggest triumph 
