<HEADLINE> `Analyze This' Rubs Out Competition / Box Office  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Five new films couldn't knock the mob comedy  
``Analyze This'' from the No. 1 spot at North American theaters. 
</P>
<P>
	The film starring Robert De Niro as a crime figure seeking help  
