	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices fell Monday on the London Stock  
Exchange. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index fell 75.4  
points, or 1.2 percent, to 6,206.8. 
</P>
<P>
	Provisional volume was 1.378 billion shares, compared with 1.079  
million shares Friday. 
</P>
