<HEADLINE> Brian Dennehy Hospitalized </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Two Broadway performances of ``Death of a  
Salesman'' were canceled because star Brian Dennehy was 
hospitalized with what his spokesman said was high blood pressure. 
</P>
