	The beefy, 59-year-old actor went to the hospital around 3 a.m.  
Sunday because he felt ill and couldn't sleep. 
</P>
<P>
	Performances Sunday and Tuesday were canceled because Dennehy,  
whose role as Willy Loman requires him to be on stage for almost 
three hours, has no understudy. 
</P>
<P>
